### Saving Grains API Testing
### Base URL for development
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "+233123456789",
  "password": "your_password"
}

### 2. Verify OTP (use OTP from login response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "+233123456789",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 3. Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone_number": "+233987654321",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "roles": ["user"]
}

### 4. Get All Users (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Create Wallet Request - Cash Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "payment_method": "Cash Payment",
  "reason": "Monthly savings deposit"
}

### 6. Create Wallet Request - Mobile Money
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 250.50,
  "payment_method": "Mobile Money",
  "provider": "MTN",
  "phone_number": "+233123456789",
  "reason": "Emergency fund deposit"
}

### 7. Create Wallet Request - Bank Transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 500.00,
  "payment_method": "Bank Transfer",
  "bank_name": "Ghana Commercial Bank",
  "branch_name": "Accra Main Branch",
  "reason": "Bulk savings transfer"
}